name: LOVE 22 - 02
description:
LOVE is an audio-visual project that consists of:

♥ LOVE music NFT (first mint under my own smart contract)
♥ LOVE Music video (second mint under my own smart contract)
♥ 22 objkts minted on Tezos in editions of 2, priced at 2.22 tez
♥ Collaborative Project: I am sharing the music stems with musicians to do a 2nd collaborative NFT drop of LOVE's remixes, splitting NFTs 50/50 on the blockchain. 

* To follow this LOVE music project head out to my website --> vjdeliria.com
 
* The LOVE NFT music project dropped on 22-2-22 and is dedicated to the two most important people in my life.
 
* Connect on Twitter @VjDeliria and say hi :)
